(112778)\">Morm. 4:10-12<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112997\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112997)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112997)\">Moro. 9:5<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">12. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"108781\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 108781)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(108781)\">John 13:27<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112274\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112274)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112274)\">Alma 40:13<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">13. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"107965\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 107965)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(107965)\">Matt. 12:31<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">14. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112253\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112253)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112253)\">Alma 39:6<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">15. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111520\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111520)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111520)\">Mosiah 2:37<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111761\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111761)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111761)\">Alma 3:18<\/a><\/span>;\n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"112096\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 112096)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(112096)\">Alma 30:42<\/a><\/span>\n    <\/div>\n    <div class=\"footnote\">16. \n      <span class=\"citation\" id=\"111115\"><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"sx(this, 111115)\">&nbsp;<\/a><a href=\"javascript:void(0)\" onclick=\"gs(111